     A                                      OVRDTA
     A                                      OVRATR
     A N99                                  DSPATR(ND)
     A                                 24  4'KEY ENTRY'
     A                                 24 15' CMD-3 ' DSPATR(RI)
     A                                 24 25'UPDATE'
     A                                 24 33' CMD-5 ' DSPATR(RI)
     A                                 24 43'CHANGE ENTERED NO. OF BOXES'
     A                                 24 73' CMD-7 ' DSPATR(RI)
